article.description: — Matt Knowling had 22 points in Yale's 73-44 win over Vermont on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Knowling's 22 lead Yale over Vermont 73-44
article.story: NEW HAVEN, Conn. -- — Matt Knowling had 22 points in Yale's 73-44 win over Vermont on Tuesday night. Knowling also added six rebounds for the Bulldogs (6-0). John Poulakidas scored 10 points and added five rebounds. EJ Jarvis finished 4 of 6 from the field to finish with 10 points. The Bulldogs picked up their sixth straight win. The Catamounts (1-5) were led in scoring by Matt Veretto, who finished with 12 points and two steals. Aaron Deloney added eight points for Vermont. In addition, Nick Fiorillo had six points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
